A fully functional Java Swing-based Notepad Editor that offers a rich set of features including syntax template loading, font customization, word wrap, and even an integrated Command Prompt launcher. Built as a beginner-friendly code editor for multiple languages such as Java, C, C++, Python, and HTML.

